title: Let's Eat Chocolate! (Peanut M&M's and BarkThins)
description: Welcome to episode 194 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! This episode I eat peanut M&M's and pretzel BarkThins in this rendition of "Let's Eat!" Enjoy!
